                         Family Ledger Install Overview                         

Required Software
-----------------

On Microsoft Windows: Windows XP or later.

If running the Python scripts directly, Python 3.4.4 is the minimum recommended
version.

Quick Start: Microsoft Windows
------------------------------

Unzip the downloaded Zip file, then double click on the executable or open a 
Command Prompt in the executable's directory and run either:

  ledger.exe

OR

  ledger_web.exe
  
Follow the on-screen instructions.

For more detailed information about the application, please see the 
Documentation included in the 'doc' directory or available online at: 
https://familyledger.readthedocs.io